title: why
pid: 7cc9d769-b458-4899-81c5-e074a3263536
body: |2-
  If each note is to advance some thesis|question|agenda,
  and while reading you question why you're doing it,
  finding what links to this note gives purpose to it,
  because a link source advances some other thesis|question|agenda.
misc:
- Had_ID_Before_Import
